a3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=416 416w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=632 632w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=700 700w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=800 800w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=900 900w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=1000 1000w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=1200 1200w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=1400 1400w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=1600 1600w, //zap-main.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/03-profile-01_4737ad9f-ec91-4fa5-aa8b-b26b5ffcbaa3.jpg?v=1772378079&amp;width=1800 1800w\" width=\"1856\" height=\"2262\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1440px) calc(416px * 1), (min-width: 1200px) calc(29vw * 1), (min-width: 750px) calc(48vw * 1), (min-width: 576px) calc(95vw * 1), calc(91vw * 1)\" class=\"card-grid__card-img\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\">\n</div><div class=\"card-grid__card-content card-grid__card-content--center\"><span class=\"card-grid__card-heading h4\">\n                    Amara Diallo\n                  </span><span class=\"card-grid__card-subheading body-small\">\n                    CO-FOUNDER\n                  </span><p class=\"card-grid__card-description body-small\">\n                    I've always believed that the most beautiful things grow in the space between intention and patience. What we're building here isn't just about what we 